izations</a> <span class=\"fn\">M</span> <span class=\"fn\">↑<span class=\"fn\">x</span></span></span>)</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"The functions satisfying `isLocallyFraction` form a submodule. ","docLink":"./Mathlib/AlgebraicGeometry/StructureSheaf.html#AlgebraicGeometry.StructureSheaf.sectionsSubmodule","kind":"def","line":117,"name":"AlgebraicGeometry.StructureSheaf.sectionsSubmodule","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/0f1dd7505c3d08b5feb82300ccc73179a457bf51/Mathlib/AlgebraicGeometry/StructureSheaf.lean#L117-L133"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/AlgebraicGeometry/StructureSheaf.html#AlgebraicGeometry.StructureSheaf.isLocallyFraction\"><span class=\"name\">AlgebraicGeometry</span>.<span class=\"name\">StructureSheaf</span>.<span class=\"name\">isLocallyFraction</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">R </span><span class=\"fn\">M</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u)</span></span>\n<span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Algebra/Ring/Defs.html#CommRing\">CommRing</a> <span class=\"fn\">R</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Algebra/Group/Defs.html#AddCommGroup\">AddCommGroup</a> <span class=\"fn\">M</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Algebra/Module/Defs.html#Module\">Module</a> <span class=\"fn\">R</span> <span class=\"fn\">M</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Topology/Sheaves/LocalPredicate.html#TopCat.LocalPredicate\">TopCat.LocalPredicate</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Mathlib/AlgebraicGeometry/StructureSheaf.html#AlgebraicGeometry.StructureSheaf.Localizations\">Localizations</a> <span class=\"fn\">M</span>)</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"We will define the structure sheaf as\nthe subsheaf of all dependent functions in `Π x : U, Localizations R x`\nconsisting of those functions which can locally be expressed as a ratio of\n(the images in the localization of) elements of `R`.\n\nQuoting Hartshorne:\n\nFor an open set $U ⊆ Spec A$, we define $𝒪(U)$ to be the set of functions\n$s : U → ⨆_{𝔭 ∈ U} A_𝔭$, such that $s(𝔭) ∈ A_𝔭$ for each $𝔭$,\nand such that $s$ is locally a quotient of elements of $A$:\nto be precise, we require that for each $𝔭 ∈ U$, there is a neighborhood $V$ of $𝔭$,\ncontained in $U$, and elements $a, f ∈ A$, such that for each $𝔮 ∈ V, f ∉ 𝔮$,\nand $s(𝔮) = a/f$ in $A_𝔮$.\n\nNow Hartshorne had the disadvantage of not knowing about dependent functions,\nso we replace his circumlocution about functions into a disjoint union with\n`Π x : U, Localizations x`.\n","docLink":"./Mathlib/AlgebraicGeometry/StructureSheaf.html#AlgebraicGeometry.StructureSheaf.isLocallyFraction","kind":"def","line":94,"name":"AlgebraicGeometry.StructureSheaf.isLocallyFraction","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/0f1dd7505c3d08b5feb82300ccc73179a457bf51/Mathlib/AlgebraicGeometry/StructureSheaf.lean#L94-L113"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/AlgebraicGeometry/StructureSheaf.html#AlgebraicGeometry.StructureSheaf.isFractionPrelocal\"><span class=\"name\">AlgebraicGeometry</span>.<span class=\"name\">StructureSheaf</span>.<span class=\"name\">isFractionPrelocal</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">R </span><span class=\"fn\">M</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u)</span></span>\n<span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Algebra/Ring/Defs.html#CommRing\">CommRing</a> <span class=\"fn\">R</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Algebra/Group/Defs.html#AddCommGroup\">AddCommGroup</a> <span class=\"fn\">M</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Algebra/Module/Defs.html#Module\">Module</a> <span class=\"fn\">R</span> <span class=\"fn\">M</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Topology/Sheaves/LocalPredicate.html#TopCat.PrelocalPredicate\">TopCat.PrelocalPredicate</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Mathlib/AlgebraicGeometry/StructureSheaf.html#AlgebraicGeometry.StructureSheaf.Localizations\">Localizations</a> <span class=\"fn\">M</span>)</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"The predicate `IsFraction` is \"prelocal\",\nin the sense that if it holds on `U` it holds on any open subset `V` of `U`.\n","docLink":"./Mathlib/AlgebraicGeometry/StructureSheaf.html#AlgebraicGeometry.StructureSheaf.isFractionPrelocal","kind":"def","line":86,"name":"AlgebraicGeometry.StructureSheaf.isFractionPrelocal","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/0f1dd7505c3d08b5feb82300ccc73179a457bf51/Mathlib/AlgebraicGeometry/StructureSheaf.lean#L86-L91"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/AlgebraicGeometry/StructureSheaf.html#AlgebraicGeometry.StructureSheaf.IsFraction\"><span class=\"name\">AlgebraicGeometry</span>.<span class=\"name\">StructureSheaf</span>.<span class=\"name\">IsFraction</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<s